Class PanelRunner

    • java.awt.Component

  • All Implemented Interfaces:

    Direct Known Subclasses:
    PanelRunner_Animated, PanelRunner_AnimatedFromStates, PanelRunner_Comparison, PanelRunner_MultiState, PanelRunner_SimpleState, PanelRunner_Snapshot, TreeWorker
    public abstract class PanelRunner
extends javax.swing.JPanel
implements IUserInterface.TabbedPaneActivator
    Snapshot viewers of the runner and animations of the runner share a lot of features and dimensions. Hence, this superclass handles certain shared drawing processes.
    Author:
    matt
